{"tid":943533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又贏] 中國將再買300萬噸美國粟米","createTime":"2018-12-16T14:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T16:04:57.000Z","uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"012ff2cd5c81d73176e4073fe18ddca9f790e3d6","tid":943533,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T14:50:23.000Z","msg":"中國將再買300萬噸美國粟米<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b/article/20181216/s00013/1544897298720/%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%b0%87%e5%86%8d%e8%b2%b7300%e8%90%ac%e5%99%b8%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e7%b2%9f%e7%b1%b3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%2Farticle%2F20181216%2Fs00013%2F1544897298720%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%25b0%2587%25e5%2586%258d%25e8%25b2%25b7300%25e8%2590%25ac%25e5%2599%25b8%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e7%25b2%259f%25e7%25b1%25b3&d=QRiv9YnaLWrwMBsY1jL0JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e0d87f49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%2Farticle%2F20181216%2Fs00013%2F1544897298720%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%25b0%2587%25e5%2586%258d%25e8%25b2%25b7300%25e8%2590%25ac%25e5%2599%25b8%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e7%25b2%259f%25e7%25b1%25b3&h=e18c67cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b/article/20181216/s00013/1544897298720/%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%b0%87%e5%86%8d%e8%b2%b7300%e8%90%ac%e5%99%b8%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e7%b2%9f%e7%b1%b3</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】彭博社引述兩名消息人士報道，在購買美國大豆之後，中方正準備在1月左右購買300萬噸美國粟米。消息人士指，由於美國大豆、粟米明年起將陸續付運，中國當局也正考慮調整對美國農產品的懲罰性關稅，但現時未有正式方案。<br />\n<br />\n此外，美國貿易代表辦公室正式將針對中國2000億美元產品提高關稅的時間，從2019年1月1日改為美國東區標準時間2019年3月2日午夜12點零1分（香港時間3月2日下午1時零1分）。路透社報道，美國原本計劃從2019年1月1日起將目前針對中國2000億美元產品實施的10%關稅提高到25%，但是兩國元首12月1日在阿根廷會晤後，雙方決定在未來90天內舉行實質性磋商。美國貿易代表辦公室在對新關稅方案生效時間做出修改時，沒有提到美中經貿磋商需要達到什麼結果才能避免新關稅的實施。"},{"pid":"7c078a243056bca80b45c27eedfdffb354cb0957","tid":943533,"uid":117679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T14:52:23.000Z","msg":"美國輸了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俾中國買起咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52bd3cf538c5689b755e05f924d123afeb755c6","tid":943533,"uid":38546,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T14:53:42.000Z","msg":"買到美國人連粟米湯都無得飲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36b4d9cd4fafc7aa558754bdf2c1bff7f04ab81","tid":943533,"uid":108337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T15:02:29.000Z","msg":"中國食粟米<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b26bc32bf955536e81e6bf95037c51534047ef2","tid":943533,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T15:25:55.000Z","msg":"中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847f11dd0ed6c8ab87f2e102748cca2c809e008a","tid":943533,"uid":153778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T15:48:34.000Z","msg":"買到佢地冇粟米做粟米片早餐，又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3634c7e8af7b3039e5a70495bf40ab2c941dba","tid":943533,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T15:49:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></div></span>"},{"pid":"032515cf2db4b1e868d3ad166c1dfb9e36cffe44","tid":943533,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T16:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jdf6QKs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJdf6QKs.jpg&h=27048712&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}